---
const links = [
  {
    label: "Email",
    value: "arturo@example.com",
    href: "mailto:arturoale1994@gmail.com",
    icon: "M4 4h16v16H4V4zm0 0l8 8 8-8",
  },
  {
    label: "WhatsApp",
    value: "Escribime directo",
    href: "https://wa.me/+5592996245264",
    icon: "M4 4h16v16H4V4zm0 0l8 8 8-8",
  },
  {
    label: "GitHub",
    value: "A2calanche",
    href: "https://github.com/A2calanche",
    icon: "M4 4h16v16H4V4zm0 0l8 8 8-8",
  },
  {
    label: "LinkedIn",
    value: "/in/arturo-calanche",
    href: "https://linkedin.com/in/arturo-calanche",
    icon: "M4 4h16v16H4V4zm0 0l8 8 8-8",
  },
];
---

<section id="contact" class="contact">
  <div class="contact__inner">
    <h2>Contacto</h2>
    <p class="contact__intro">
      ¿Tenés un proyecto en mente o una oportunidad para conversar? Escribime
      por cualquiera de estos medios.
    </p>

    <div class="contact__grid">
      {links.map((link) => (
        <a
          class="contact__card"
          href={link.href}
          target={link.href.startsWith("http") ? "_blank" : undefined}
          rel={link.href.startsWith("http") ? "noopener noreferrer" : undefined}
        >
          <span class="contact__label">{link.label}</span>
          <span class="contact__value">{link.value}</span>
        </a>
      ))}
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .contact {
    padding-block: 4rem 6rem;
  }

  .contact__inner {
    max-width: 42rem;
    margin-inline: auto;
    padding-inline: 1.5rem;
    text-align: center;
  }

  h2 {
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }

  .contact__intro {
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
  }

  .contact__grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(11rem, 1fr));
    gap: 1rem;
  }

  .contact__card {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.25rem;
    padding: 1.25rem;
    border-radius: 1rem;
    background: var(--glass-bg, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08));
    backdrop-filter: blur(var(--glass-blur, 12px)) saturate(var(--glass-sat, 180%));
    -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(var(--glass-blur, 12px)) saturate(var(--glass-sat, 180%));
    border: 1px solid var(--glass-border, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.18));
    color: inherit;
    text-decoration: none;
    text-align: left;
    transition: transform 200ms ease, border-color 200ms ease;
  }

  .contact__card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-3px);
    border-color: var(--color-accent);
  }

  .contact__label {
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.06em;
    color: var(--color-accent-text, var(--color-accent));
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .contact__value {
    color: var(--color-text);
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    word-break: break-word;
  }
</style>